    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you decide to purchase. The exterior shows its age \u2014 you'll notice several scratches and minor dents consistent with years of regular use, and the paint has faded in spots. The interior is functional but worn: the upholstery has visible scuffs and staining, and some trim pieces show cracking. Mechanically, the engine starts and runs, but you should expect that some components are aging and may require attention in the near future \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection by your own mechanic. This is a solid option for a buyer who needs reliable basic transportation and is comfortable with a vehicle that has cosmetic imperfections and may need occasional maintenance. Priced fairly to reflect its true condition.",
