    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and I want to be completely upfront about that before you inquire. The car has significant mechanical issues that will require substantial repair work \u2014 it is not currently reliable for daily driving and should be considered a project vehicle or parts car depending on your needs. The exterior shows heavy wear including rust, dents, and faded or damaged paint, and the interior is in rough shape with torn upholstery, broken components, and general deterioration throughout. That said, the price reflects the condition honestly, and this could be a worthwhile opportunity for a skilled mechanic or someone looking for a restoration project. Please reach out with any questions \u2014 I'd rather you have the full picture than be surprised after purchase.",
